{"type": "article", "id": 5382, "title": "Normann Copenhagen Form 系列家具", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-20T07:29:41Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 4, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606141235yqG05t7sLFMl3WU4.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t在 Normann Copenhagen 的品牌价值观里，唯有兼具现代与简洁特质的家具才不会过时。结合功能、美学与简洁 3 个要素，设计师 Simon Legald 带来了这一系列名为「Form」的百搭款桌椅，包括有扶手与无扶手的两款椅子、一款吧椅以及尺寸不同的两张桌子。 Simon Legald 为椅腿与桌腿选择了美国橡木与胡桃木两种材质，既耐磨也适合于多种家居风格，经过手工打磨后与椅面与桌面焊接在一起，省去了螺丝钉。Form 系列将亮相本周开幕的巴黎家具装饰博览会，定价 300－2400 美元（约合人民币 1865－14921 元）不等，<a href=\"http://www.normann-copenhagen.com/families/form\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141233ZgoO6H0Atiqe4kXz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141233MsASmt9VolbnCdGk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141234Oyop7z6g4varNjJ0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061412345UDhJTo3sE9CgW6j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141235xcpgtzICB8SJoiqH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}